Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.20,0:01:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前如果慊人或父亲下令的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.47,0:01:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是谁都要消除记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.97,0:01:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然明知这样会伤害由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.61,0:01:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我还是把他的朋友的记忆消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.68,0:01:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像雪一样寒冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.72,0:01:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人当时所说的话或许是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.99,0:01:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙又出去了 到处都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是说小透吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.53,0:02:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她到朋友家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.57,0:02:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天吃晚饭的时候就说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.30,0:02:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.01,0:02:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你从来不听别人说话的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.51,0:02:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少啰唆！她很少出门的嘛 都怪她不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.78,0:02:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透已经很习惯这个家了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.12,0:02:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吾家花儿今在何方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.89,0:02:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.89,0:02:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…好大哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩家果然家大业大…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.43,0:02:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然是为了草摩同学他们的秘密而来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.80,0:02:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 或许能见到当家的慊人先生哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.71,0:02:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.71,0:02:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红…红叶 危、危险！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.68,0:02:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很准时哦 门没关 进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打扰了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.29,0:02:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎来到草摩家！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.33,0:03:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！里面也好大哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.13,0:03:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,门里面好像一个小镇一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像来到一个未知的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.87,0:03:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是好安静哦 好像没有住人似的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.88,0:03:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种气氛让我更紧张了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.15,0:03:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边这边 波鸟住在更里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.29,0:03:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很怕波鸟吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 不、不会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.16,0:03:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很喜欢他哦 你应该也会很喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要拘束 放轻松点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…好的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然他这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.07,0:03:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过这种气氛令我更紧张了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照片？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.65,0:03:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到这里会有女人的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.45,0:03:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在有点意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.12,0:04:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看上去那么严肃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.99,0:04:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…他说有很重要的事情要说 莫非是要骂我!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住在这么气派的豪邸的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.53,0:04:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然不想跟住在帐篷里的我有任何瓜葛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.77,0:04:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这样冒冒失失的 真的是太失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透？你是不是哪里不舒服？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让波鸟看看吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他可是个医生哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没、没关系 我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.28,0:04:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽说是医生 也只不过是草摩家的主治大夫而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.49,0:04:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且有一半的时间都在照顾慊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙的专长就是容易生病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.76,0:04:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不喜欢拐弯抹角 我们就开门见山的说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…好的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道十二生肖秘密的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.67,0:04:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我们家族中也只是少数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.04,0:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你这个外人知道这个秘密实在很不像话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.31,0:05:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本应该立即消除你的记忆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过慊人并没有下达这项指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,允许你和他们一起住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.19,0:05:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在紫吴家生活还快乐吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…是的…很快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我劝你还是尽早搬出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.59,0:05:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再和草摩家有任何瓜葛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.73,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离开紫吴的家 回到亲戚的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.93,0:05:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这才是你原本的生活吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.80,0:05:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴那家伙应该什么也没告诉你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.21,0:05:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被怪物附身的草摩家并没有你想像的那么快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.01,0:05:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诡异…阴森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.45,0:05:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还被诅咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被诅咒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.36,0:05:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你后悔与草摩家有任何关联之前…搬走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.20,0:05:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟 我想带小透到庭院里走走可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.84,0:05:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.34,0:05:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.81,0:06:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我带你到我喜欢的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.15,0:06:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩家并没有你想像的那么快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.56,0:06:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诡异…阴森…还被诅咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.59,0:06:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很安静吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.79,0:06:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊、是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.53,0:06:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩家的人今天都为了正月而在内院里做准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正月的时候大家都会聚在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.67,0:06:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是很重要的节日 忙死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.51,0:06:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从大门外林荫道到本家这一带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.54,0:06:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住的人全都是草摩家的人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.92,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？那不是很多人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.22,0:06:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴和由希以前也住在这里哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.29,0:06:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能住在这里的人不是像我一样是十二生肖之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.36,0:06:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是知道这个秘密的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.90,0:07:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你这个外人知道这个秘密实在很不像话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.74,0:07:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟的左眼几乎看不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.74,0:07:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.84,0:07:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟有一个情人叫做佳菜 她是波鸟的助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个很好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使知道波鸟被怪物附身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也只是若无其事的笑笑而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.12,0:07:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们还订下婚约…不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人很生气 非常生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他反对这椿婚事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动手使波鸟的眼睛受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.13,0:07:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而波鸟并没有责怪慊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.21,0:07:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是佳菜却十分自责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.34,0:07:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她怪自己害波鸟的眼睛受伤…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.75,0:07:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不断的自责 使她得了心病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.55,0:07:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟不得已将佳菜的记忆消除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不忍心看佳菜变得那么憔悴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.99,0:08:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于是把两人相爱的时光消掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.77,0:08:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佳菜离开这里的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.54,0:08:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是他并不怪慊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.08,0:08:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这是诅咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.05,0:08:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…我多少能够了解波鸟的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.96,0:08:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不希望再看到有人会变得和佳菜一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.36,0:08:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不希望你受到和佳菜一样的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.13,0:08:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？小透？你在哭吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我害你哭的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉、真的很抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.74,0:08:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.58,0:08:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我哭是因为波鸟先生太温柔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.32,0:09:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他还为我的事担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在需要这份温柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.73,0:09:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许是波鸟先生才对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.70,0:09:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去帮你倒杯热茶 进来里面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道会下雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.56,0:09:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.63,0:09:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对草摩家的事一无所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你用不着知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.70,0:09:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好还是忘掉比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.94,0:09:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘掉了吗？波鸟先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.78,0:10:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你用不着道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.22,0:10:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有机会的话 我也会和佳菜见面、聊天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过仅止于此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能够了解我的意思吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天说得太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没、没有这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且…我…还要再回那个家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.70,0:10:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水！不 海、海水!?还是水？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.10,0:10:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底什么才好？波鸟先生～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.85,0:11:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面 我是草摩佳菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天开始担任你的助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会好好努力的 请多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是同一个家族的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是却从来没有说过话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 波鸟先生人很帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在朋友之中也很受欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里就是你的桌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.57,0:11:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是你今天的工作 快点做吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.44,0:11:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！是雪 我就知道会下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.21,0:11:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以问你一个问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.84,0:11:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪融化之后会变成什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.91,0:11:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那还用说 当然是水罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.25,0:11:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对！会变成春天哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.55,0:11:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最喜欢春天了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.63,0:11:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人只要有了感情就能把别人美化…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.70,0:12:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我来说 她就是我的春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.20,0:12:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在幽暗紧闭的草摩家中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.17,0:12:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永远都像被冰冷的雪封住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.14,0:12:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但对我来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.35,0:12:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她就像鲜绿蓬勃的春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.69,0:12:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们爱就像是命中注定的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我的梦也开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水！不！海水!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.34,0:12:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底要哪一种？波鸟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有件事我要事先说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把龙的私生子丢到浴缸里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可能会害死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我不知道该怎么办啊 只好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过…我终于知道原因了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还在想你为什么不让我抱你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.06,0:13:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你害怕 不想让人家知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以和别人保持距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.07,0:13:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是喜欢的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.41,0:13:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过你不用怕 不要拒绝我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.48,0:13:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…能够遇到你 觉得很开心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能喜欢波鸟是一件幸福的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.62,0:13:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望能留在你身边…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流泪了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.39,0:13:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仿佛出生以来第一次有人原谅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.66,0:13:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次有人救我的心情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.03,0:13:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像春天的气息吹得冻结的雪融化一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我泪流不止…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.51,0:13:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就像在做梦一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.18,0:13:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像凝聚了几十年的幸福一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.45,0:13:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们想要结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行！我不准你们结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不准！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.60,0:14:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟？你怎么了？波鸟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是你害的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.40,0:14:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是波鸟看不见的话 全都是你害的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.51,0:14:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人！波鸟!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.78,0:14:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以解开草摩家的诅咒吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佳菜 快点把波鸟带走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有办法解开诅咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.88,0:14:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你有什么用！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你有什么用！全都是你害的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.26,0:14:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都是你害的！全都是你害的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.47,0:14:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管我说什么、做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她只是一味的哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.34,0:14:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后她病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.01,0:15:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的隐蔽术这时候应该可以派上用场吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应该消除她的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.48,0:15:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前你不是很干净俐落的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.19,0:15:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在令她痛苦的是和你的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对你的爱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.49,0:15:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够将她从痛苦之中解救出来的只有你而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是你最后的功用啊 波鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她也希望能真正获得解脱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.81,0:15:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果没有相逢就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她求你忘掉她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.28,0:15:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果没有相逢…就好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.82,0:15:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是否会对别人造成伤害 也不管对方是否哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.32,0:15:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要接到命令就会将别人的记忆消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.09,0:15:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是万万没想到自己最重要的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最重要的回忆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要由自己下手消除…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是报应啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.51,0:16:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你 佳菜 已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再也不会觉得痛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.28,0:16:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总有一天你会想找一个能够给你幸福的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.02,0:16:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我只能默默祝福你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.62,0:16:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.53,0:16:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起…我不能保护你 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.01,0:16:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该道歉的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能保护你的人也是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够与你相逢 我很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.46,0:16:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够遇到你 我很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.86,0:16:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的一生都在不会融化的雪中渡过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.53,0:17:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望我们做过的梦永远不会融化…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.94,0:17:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你的照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.24,0:17:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于你的指导 让我得以成为医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.31,0:17:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然只是个菜鸟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.22,0:17:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救救波鸟先生吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.07,0:17:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能够遇到大家 觉得很幸运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不想失去和他们的关系…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佳菜小姐应该也是这么想的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.84,0:17:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 救救波鸟先生吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.52,0:17:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊、我没有看 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道该怎么办才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.66,0:17:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以先把你移到房间来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.56,0:18:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你躺在那里 冒昧地用我的脏大衣盖住你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后 然后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.76,0:18:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看到了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.13,0:18:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有！然后 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的十二生肖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…是啊 很可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很令人意外哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.08,0:18:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之 你没事 我也就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.38,0:18:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…这个…很抱歉 我擅自…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.75,0:18:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经有好一阵子没有做梦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这场雪的关系吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 我可以问你一个问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪融化之后会变成什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.90,0:18:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…嗯 这个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会变成春天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管现在多么冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.24,0:18:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,春天总是会来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.41,0:18:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不可思议呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.85,0:18:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪一定会融化的 一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.35,0:18:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最喜欢春天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.69,0:19:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你冷不冷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.59,0:19:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.02,0:19:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 我也很喜欢充满食欲的秋天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.23,0:19:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们去买个热腾腾的东西吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？热腾腾的东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,热茶好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦!?紫吴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.44,0:19:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉呀～找你好久了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找到了一只迷路的兔子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.34,0:19:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶！啊 不是热茶是果汁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你久等了 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.42,0:19:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.59,0:19:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你来做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.56,0:19:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.02,0:19:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怕你会吓到小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.33,0:19:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艺术家的第六感嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.20,0:19:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少来了 你是来看正月的准备的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们两个虽然常顶嘴却是好朋友喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.40,0:19:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌 凡人就是会忌妒天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有没有问波鸟的生肖呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.28,0:19:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴 你希望四岁时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.11,0:20:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爱哭鬼的可笑模样在出版界流传吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了啦 我不说就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正一下就被识破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.98,0:20:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.68,0:20:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.65,0:20:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不认为这有什么好丢脸的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.49,0:20:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好温暖哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天让你添麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过波鸟不是什么坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.94,0:20:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道 他很温柔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.86,0:20:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚、刚刚莫非是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.00,0:20:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透？离我太远你会迷路哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴 诅咒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.91,0:21:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诅咒到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.67,0:21:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没有我能够帮上忙的地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.84,0:21:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心 你只要扮演好自己就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天知道了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过也有很多事不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.69,0:21:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不可思议的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.06,0:21:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回来罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.69,0:21:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.16,0:21:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 回来晚了…咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.47,0:21:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,俗话说得好 暖炉桌连鬼都好睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.71,0:21:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.24,0:21:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是把他们叫醒的话有点危险 还是暂时别理他们好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.04,0:21:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.01,0:21:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 不管是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.98,0:21:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都很珍惜 这样的心情依旧没有改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够在这个家生活的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.89,0:21:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会很珍惜 很珍惜…

